title: Grateful Greens Gourmet Chopped Salads
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Local business offering fresh, healthy chopped salads and wraps. Could create your own salad by choosing the greens, ingredients, and dressing; has tofu and vegan taco meat. Several lacto-veg panini sandwiches, a hummus and pbj sandwich, and tofu sandwich on request. Hours, menu items, prices are subject to change, check Facebook for more details.
